precis:
Regulations Amending the NEW SUBSTANCES NOTIFICATION REGULATIONS whereby
those who import or manufacture new substances that are organisms,
biochemicals or biopolymers, for purposes not otherwise addressed under
any other federal statute, will be required to submit a notification to
Environment Canada.
